{"tid":880931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少林寺弟子43秒KO非洲拳王？拳王身份被踢爆","createTime":"2018-10-29T05:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:26:11.000Z","uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"151cca6cf5ad384be2460adc49ebc2a17f8960b0","tid":880931,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpSzYgAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpSzYgAH.jpg&h=c6708ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-10-28 08:24<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕為宣揚少林寺武功蓋天下，在中國「功夫之都」河南登封舉辦一場「武極天下&middot;登封造極」世界格鬥冠軍賽，其中一場少林弟子釋延孜迎戰非洲職業拳王蓋博瑞之戰，吸引約3萬名觀眾現場觀戰，釋延孜以43秒時間直接KO非洲拳王，當場中國觀眾歡聲雷動，但是，事後卻被網友踢爆，這名非洲拳王只是被雇用打拳的非洲留學生。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，蓋博瑞已經承認自己根本不是什麼非洲拳王，宣傳所說的15戰中14勝1負也是假的，他承認，<span style=\"color: red;\">自己只是一名在中國的留學生，就讀於瀋陽航空航天大學，被雇用打拳，曾在中國打過6場拳賽，只贏過1場，但今年初已離校。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於打贏拳賽的釋延孜也被起底，是少林寺第34代弟子，是少林寺方丈釋永信的親傳弟子，在1988年就拿到過全國武術散打錦標賽冠軍，也是英國少林寺的掌門人，是少林寺的實戰弟子。<br />\n<br />\n這場拳賽登場幾乎是一面倒的賽程，30歲的蓋博瑞對釋延孜的拳腿攻擊，但顯得軟弱無力，而延後，51歲的釋延孜就一拳打中蓋博瑞腹部，蓋博瑞倒在台上，前後才43秒就結束賽局。<br />\n<br />\n被揪出作假，主辦單位也承認，在選手挑選審核存在紕漏，將來也擔補救措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2594283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2594283&d=qmI7%2FJfYZh2CmzOCciuMjC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bba3dd75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2594283&h=44140d32\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2594283</a>"},{"pid":"5fcb03e9cc3ecba0c77a5abb7246045865ba9a48","tid":880931,"uid":137732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea37e151737da459bda551ac8e08153081ec447e","tid":880931,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"打個普通留學生都要43秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我肯定做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f57594e6168a3efab356d481c203046d16f73e0","tid":880931,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"至於打贏拳賽的釋延孜也被起底，是少林寺第34代弟子，是少林寺方丈釋永信的親傳弟子，在1988年就拿到過全國武術散打錦標賽冠軍，也是英國少林寺的掌門人，是少林寺的實戰弟子。<br />\n<br />\n咁都要43秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471cf6bb522d009ea70c74c01581290437bbd7c5","tid":880931,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"上面張相真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWong咁嘅格一拳打到黑鬼KO,一定係用魔法"},{"pid":"d8524cab601582243f7d179b3344de2c61c7a715","tid":880931,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"471cf6bb522d009ea70c74c01581290437bbd7c5","tid":880931,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"上面張相真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWong咁嘅格一拳打到黑鬼KO,一定係用魔法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"假拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}